'''迈克尔·杰克逊不朽传奇世界巡演'''（{{lang-en|''Michael Jackson: The Immortal World Tour''}}）是[[太阳马戏团|太阳马戏团]]使用[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]的音乐与舞步打造的一场全球巡回演出的舞台剧，由{{tsl|en|Jamie King|杰米·金}}编导<ref name=NYT>{{cite web |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |title=Singing Pageant of Pop, With a Circus Atmosphere |author=Webster, Andy |date=April 2, 2012 |url=http://theater.nytimes.com/2012/04/03/theater/reviews/michael-jackson-the-immortal-world-tour-cirque-du-soleil.html?_r=0}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cirquedusoleil.com/en/press/news/2011/mj-premiere-october-tonight-in-montreal.aspx |title=World Premiere Tonight in Montreal! |accessdate=2012-01-17 |date=2011-10-02 |publisher=Cirque du Soleil |work=Cirque du Soleil Press Release |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124040603/http://www.cirquedusoleil.com/en/press/news/2011/mj-premiere-october-tonight-in-montreal.aspx |archive-date=2012-01-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。该舞台剧的形式与[[演唱会|演唱会]]非常相似。巡演的首场于2011年10月2日在加拿大[[蒙特利尔|蒙特利尔]]举行，团队在[[北美洲|北美洲]]演出一年之后，又抵达[[欧洲|欧洲]]、[[亚洲|亚洲]]、[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]和[[中东地区|中东地区]]进行巡回演出，后于2014年2月回到北美洲，2014年8月31日演出结束。此次演出乃[[太阳马戏团|太阳马戏团]]票房最高的一场全球巡回演出。

2011年12月，演出开始两个月之后已经在美国和加拿大卖出了超过1亿美元的门票，根据[[福布斯|福布斯]]，其已成为在美国的顶级巡回演出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2011/12/12/why-michael-jackson-is-the-top-touring-act-in-america-again/ |title=Why Michael Jackson Is The Top Touring Act In America, Again |date=12 December 2011 |accessdate=7 January 2014 |archive-date=2021-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421043745/https://www.forbes.com/sites/zackomalleygreenburg/2011/12/12/why-michael-jackson-is-the-top-touring-act-in-america-again/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年8月31日在27个国家的巡演结束之后，总票房为3.71亿美元<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.facebook.com/michaeljackson/photos/a.108910151472.86254.19691681472/10152786782171473/?type=1&theater|title=Michael Jackson Immortal Tour Wraps With $371 million and 3.7 million ticket sold worldwide|work=Cirque/Michael Jackson Estate|publisher=Michael Jackson Facebook|date=October 1, 2014|accessdate=October 8, 2014}}</ref>，乃有史以来{{tsl|en|List of highest-grossing concert tours|总票房排名第七的巡演}}。

这场演出吸引了众多知名人士的观赏，如[[布萊德·彼特|布萊德·彼特]]、[[安吉丽娜·朱莉|安吉丽娜·朱莉]]<ref>[http://www.ahlanlive.com/brad-pitt-s-birthday-celebrations-with-his-family--158269.html Ahlanlive.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205215628/http://www.ahlanlive.com/brad-pitt-s-birthday-celebrations-with-his-family--158269.html |date=2012-02-05 }}</ref>、[[Jay_Z|Jay Z]]、[[碧昂絲·諾利斯|碧昂絲·諾利斯]]、[[蕾哈娜|蕾哈娜]]、[[伊娃·朗歌莉亞|伊娃·朗歌莉亞]]、[[柯特妮·考克斯|柯特妮·考克斯]]、[[喬許·葛洛班|喬許·葛洛班]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cozycot.com/enews/article/Celebrities-arrive-at-the-Staples-Center-to-watch-Michael-Jackson-163114/photo/604231 |title=Cozycot.com |accessdate=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2013-01-19 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130119171718/http://www.cozycot.com/enews/article/Celebrities-arrive-at-the-Staples-Center-to-watch-Michael-Jackson-163114/photo/604231 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、[[珍妮弗·洛佩兹|珍妮弗·洛佩兹]]<ref>[http://www.digitalspy.com/celebrity/i505503-8/celebrity-pictures-201012-261012-jennifer-lopez-and-boyfriend-casper-smart-enjoy-a-late-dinner-at-hakkasan-restaurant-following-a-trip-to-the-o2-arena-to-watch-cirque-du-soleil-michael-jackson-the-immortal-world-tour.html Digital Spy]{{Dead link|date=2019年6月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>、[[泰雅·賓絲|泰雅·賓絲]]、[[纳奥米·坎贝尔|纳奥米·坎贝尔]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2124870/Coco-Austin-Naomi-Campbell-Cirque-du-Soleils-Michael-Jackson-tribute-launch.html |title=Daily Mail |access-date=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813004850/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2124870/Coco-Austin-Naomi-Campbell-Cirque-du-Soleils-Michael-Jackson-tribute-launch.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、《[[欢乐合唱团|欢乐合唱团]]》的一些演员<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news/michael-jackson-kids-launch-hollywood-celebration-of-the-king-of-pop_1288177 |title=Contact Music |access-date=2015-06-12 |archive-date=2014-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911011222/http://www.contactmusi